00:19:41,879 --> 00:19:44,514
Thanks, Tina.
I got him right where
I want him.

470
00:19:44,516 --> 00:19:46,750
[ Chanting Continues ]
Ow!

471
00:19:46,752 --> 00:19:48,585
Keep going.
Hyah!

472
00:19:48,587 --> 00:19:50,654
Ow! Ow!

473
00:19:53,858 --> 00:19:55,992
- Hey, nice form.
- Thanks.

474
00:19:55,994 --> 00:19:59,596
Sorry Jairo
knocked you down
25 to 30 times...

475
00:19:59,598 --> 00:20:00,764
in front of everyone.

476
00:20:00,766 --> 00:20:03,800
Yeah. Sorry I couldn't get
your yellow corda.

477
00:20:03,802 --> 00:20:06,403
It's okay.
Thanks for getting
beat up for me.

478
00:20:06,405 --> 00:20:08,205
Hmm.
Anyway,
I'm kind of interested...

479
00:20:08,207 --> 00:20:09,673
in Russian kettlebell
strength training now.

480
00:20:09,675 --> 00:20:12,576
[ Bob ]
Don't make me watch this
'cause I--

481
00:20:12,578 --> 00:20:13,843
I'll show Mom.
Yeah.

482
00:20:13,845 --> 00:20:15,412
Well, I have a surprise
for you.

483
00:20:15,414 --> 00:20:17,948
You got a promotion.
Really?
I get a raise?

484
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:20,650
No, but you get
these yellow dish gloves.

485
00:20:20,652 --> 00:20:23,820
I present to you
your yellow gloves.

486
00:20:23,822 --> 00:20:25,322
So much fun.

487
00:20:25,324 --> 00:20:26,356
Well,
we better get going.

488
00:20:26,358 --> 00:20:29,426
Yeah. That dead seal
down at the pier
isn't gonna poke itself.

489
00:20:29,428 --> 00:20:30,727
Wait, wait. Hold on.

490
00:20:30,729 --> 00:20:32,529
You two are working today.
What?

491
00:20:32,531 --> 00:20:34,431
We're not on the schedule today.

492
00:20:34,433 --> 00:20:37,567
Read! Learn how to read
the schedule that you write.

493
00:20:37,569 --> 00:20:39,869
Tina, honey,
we're giving you the day off.

494
00:20:39,871 --> 00:20:43,473
Go do something fun.
Do you know where
this dead seal is?

495
00:20:43,475 --> 00:20:45,775
What's that about?
Its a dead seal, Mom.

496
00:20:45,777 --> 00:20:47,978
A washed-up seal.
They go poke at it.

497
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:50,247
And we're gonna slap it.
It makes a great sound.

498
00:20:50,249 --> 00:20:53,016
And I sample the slaps.
Sounds like an orgy.

499
00:20:53,018 --> 00:20:55,051
I like dead seals, but...

500
00:20:55,053 --> 00:20:56,886
I think I'm gonna
stay here instead.

501
00:20:56,888 --> 00:20:59,022
I'm actually having fun
at work today.

502
00:20:59,024 --> 00:21:01,591
Besides, it's our
father-daughter time.

503
00:21:01,593 --> 00:21:02,592
Aw!

504
00:21:02,594 --> 00:21:03,927
Sucker!
Gene, run.

505
00:21:03,929 --> 00:21:07,564
Run, run,
run, run,
run to the seal!

